<div class="container" style="margin-top: 40px;">
  <div class="well">
    <h1 style="margin-top: 20px;"> Contact me !</h1>
    <div style="text-align: center;">
    <p>If any question, please contact me. I'll reply as soon as possible</p>
    <p>궁금하신 점이 있으시다면 연락주세요! 촬영기기부터 촬영장소,
      등 언제든지 환영입니다. <br> 촬영문의도 받고 있습니다. 모델도 항상 구하고 있으니 부담없이
    연락주세요.</p>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <%= form_for @message, url:message_index_path do |m|%>
  <div style="padding: 0px 30px 30px 30px;">
  
    <div class="field">
      <%= m.label :email%>
      <%= m.text_field :email, required: true, style: "width: 100%;"%>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
      <%= m.label :title%>
      <%= m.text_field :title, required: true,style: "width: 100%;"%>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
      <%= m.label :message%>
      <%= m.text_area :message, required: true, style: "width: 100%; height: 200px;"%>
    </div>
    <div class="action", style="text-align: right;">
      <%= m.submit 'Send messsages', class: "button"%>
    </div>
    <%end%>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
